<bug>
    <id>TRUNK-1967</id>
    <title>Patient Search When Adding New Encounter Doesn't Finish with Complete Search Terms</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">The patient search when adding a new encounter doesn't finish with complete search terms.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">It appears the patient search triggers before the user finishes typing, and doesn't update the search results as they continue typing.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">This leads for a long list for the user to choose from, when they have given additional information to narrow the results.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">See the attached screen-shot.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
